Package: spatzli
Version: 0.99.0
Title: Methods for analyzing spatially resolved transcriptomics data
Description: Functions implementing methods to analyze spatially transcriptomics 
    data. Currently includes methods to identify spatially variable genes (SVGs) 
    and for spatially aware clustering.
